<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-2 sidebar pl-0">

      <div class="position-logo">
        <div class="d-inline-block position-img">
          <%=image_tag image_path('logo.png'), class: 'icon-xsm'%>
        </div>
        <div class="d-inline-block">
          <span class="logo">MUSe</span><br>
          <span class="logo">MAP</span>
        </div>
      </div>
<!-- genres  -->
     <ul class="genres my-1">
       <li style="white-space: inherit" class="ml-4 my-1">
         Click a country to begin exploring over 1700 genres.
       </li>
     </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-10 px-0">
      <nav class="navbar">
        <input class="" id="search-input" name="search" placeholder="Search for a country">
        <div id="about-button" class="about">ABOUT</div>
      </nav>
      <div id="map-container"></div>
    </div>

      </div>
    </div>
<!-- spotify widget  -->
<div class="container-fluid px-0">
  <div class="row no-gutters">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <iframe src="https://open.spotify.com/embed?uri=<%=@URI%>" width="100%" height="75px" frameborder="0" allowtransparency="true" allow="encrypted-media"></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- modal / about the app  -->
<div id="modal-container">
  <div class="modal-background">
    <div class="modal">
      <h2>Muse map</h2>
      <h5>This is an effort in trying to give people a way to connect with the rest of the world through music.</h5>
      <p>"A genre is credited to a country if at least 10% or so of the genre's artists come from that country,<br> so a genre can appear in multiple countries."<br>
      <span class="text-muted sm">- everynoise.com/Glenn McDonald</span><br><br>
      The map only has data for countries that Spotify has sufficient listening activity to produce useful playlists.
      </p>
      <p class="sm"><strong>Big</strong> thanks to Spotify and Glenn McDonald for making this possible.<br>
      <span class="text-muted xsm">source code: github.com/S-MORA</span></p>
      <svg class="modal-svg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="100%" preserveAspectRatio="none">
					<rect x="0" y="0" fill="none" width="905" height="372" rx="3" ry="3"></rect>
			</svg>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
